<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.4">
<l>tūnilā muṟṟattē pōntu viḷaiyāṭa</l>
<l>vāṉilā vampulī cantirā vāveṉṟu</l>
<l>nīnilā niṉpuka ḻāniṉṟa vāyartam</l>
<l>kōṉilā vakkoṭṭāy cappāṇi kuṭantaik kiṭantāṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone to the courtyard with white moonlight, having stood,</l>
<l>calling, “O bright Moon in the sky, O Candrā, come to play!,”</l>
<l>clap cappāṇi so that the king of the cowherds</l>
<l rend="indent">—who continuously praise you—</l>
<l>shines! You who reclines in Kuṭantai, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
